---
title: Saucy Teriyaki Chicken & Noodles with Fried Egg & Crispy Shallots
description: We hope you’re hungry because this dish is serving up a truckload of taste tonight! There’s hints of sweet, soy,
sriracha and oyster all together in a sticky sauce that clings to the udon noodles when fried up with chicken. Breaking
 into that glowing fried egg on top is the best way to start eating this dish. Make sure to get a big bite.

